            <ul className="text-orange-200 text-sm space-y-2 text-left">
              <li>â€¢ Pay with ETH for all transactions</li>
              <li>â€¢ Earn CLT tokens as rewards</li>
              <li>â€¢ Convert CLT back to ETH anytime</li>
              <li>â€¢ Fast Scroll Layer 2 transactions</li>
              <li>â€¢ EVM-compatible smart contracts</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <Button
            onClick={handleConnect}
            disabled={connecting}
            size="lg"
            className="bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-700 text-white px-8 py-3"
